descriptionShort: Create wonders with Pro 3D Magic Gallery.
title: Pro 3D Magic Gallery

creator: SmnWay INC
descriptionHtml:
Looking for an app to keep your photos safe and make them look better? Try Pro 3D Gallery. This gallery app allows you to make all the settings you can think of for your photos, such as exposure, brightness, contrast, saturation, shadow, and more. Utilize our powerful cropping tools to resize your images perfectly and apply various stunning filters to enhance your pictures. With the Pro 3D Gallery, you can keep your photos both better organized and more secure.

High-Quality Slideshows

Relive your cherished memories with our high-quality slideshow feature. Watch your favorite moments come to life in a seamless cinematic presentation that's just as easy to share as it is to create.

Simple Sharing to Capture Every Special Moment

With the Pro 3D Gallery, you can easily create, edit, and share your photos on social media. Capture the moments that matter—from special days to memorable years and unforgettable nights—and keep them alive in just the right way with the Pro 3D Gallery.


Pro 3D Gallery Features:

✓ Make your own albums.
✓ Write captions for your photos and videos.
✓ Sort your photos and videos by color, year, and more.
✓ View your albums in impressive 3D.
✓ Crop your photos to the size you need.
✓ Set any photo as your lock screen.
✓ Browse easily with grid view.
✓ Automatically adjusts to how you hold your device.
✓ Start scanning photos from your last view
✓ Set photos as background
✓ Auto Hide Action bar for added protection
✓ See the date on your photos for quick reference.
✓ Enjoy a unique filmstrip view.
✓ Create beautiful slideshows.
✓ Make your photos pop with white paper mode.
✓ Share your photos easily with friends and family.
